<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="265" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,547,1620,1679]" box="[151,307,1654,1679]" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">
(
<figureCitation box="[159,231,1654,1679]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1406,210,1768]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Kusala (Scodela) directa sp. nov. a. 2S abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. anal tube appendage and pygofer dorso-lateral inner ridge; d. subgenital plate, style and connective; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. style, dorsal view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, caudal view" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2608003/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">Figs 2</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[243,256,1654,1679]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="8.[151,250,1417,1439]" captionTargetBox="[184,1400,241,1342]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[151,1436,195,1395]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 5. a–d. Kusala (Kusala) viraktamathi sp. nov.; e–h. Kusala (Scodela) directa sp. nov.; i–k. Kusala (Scodela) sinuata sp. nov.; m–p. Diomma (Diomma) sangzhiensis sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2608009/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">5</figureCitation>
e–h)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1726,2003]" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,1726,1751]" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">Description.</emphasis>
Ground color yellowish-brown, lower 2/3 of face darker. Crown fore margin rounded, anteclypeus rectangular. (
<figureCitation box="[297,367,1762,1787]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="8.[151,250,1417,1439]" captionTargetBox="[184,1400,241,1342]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[151,1436,195,1395]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 5. a–d. Kusala (Kusala) viraktamathi sp. nov.; e–h. Kusala (Scodela) directa sp. nov.; i–k. Kusala (Scodela) sinuata sp. nov.; m–p. Diomma (Diomma) sangzhiensis sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2608009/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">Figs 5</figureCitation>
e–h)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1726,2003]" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">
Male 2S abdominal apodemes (
<figureCitation box="[561,643,1798,1823]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1406,210,1768]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Kusala (Scodela) directa sp. nov. a. 2S abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. anal tube appendage and pygofer dorso-lateral inner ridge; d. subgenital plate, style and connective; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. style, dorsal view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, caudal view" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2608003/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">Fig. 2a</figureCitation>
) extended to middle of sternite IV. Anal tube appendage (
<figureCitation box="[1312,1427,1798,1823]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1406,210,1768]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Kusala (Scodela) directa sp. nov. a. 2S abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. anal tube appendage and pygofer dorso-lateral inner ridge; d. subgenital plate, style and connective; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. style, dorsal view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, caudal view" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2608003/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">Figs 2b, c</figureCitation>
) relatively short.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1726,2003]" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">
Subgenital plate (
<figureCitation box="[395,474,1870,1895]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1406,210,1768]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Kusala (Scodela) directa sp. nov. a. 2S abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. anal tube appendage and pygofer dorso-lateral inner ridge; d. subgenital plate, style and connective; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. style, dorsal view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, caudal view" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2608003/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">Fig. 2e</figureCitation>
) very broad basally. Apical part of style (
<figureCitation box="[936,1013,1870,1895]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1406,210,1768]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Kusala (Scodela) directa sp. nov. a. 2S abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. anal tube appendage and pygofer dorso-lateral inner ridge; d. subgenital plate, style and connective; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. style, dorsal view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, caudal view" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2608003/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">Fig. 2f</figureCitation>
) straight, subapical extension slightly curved basad. Connective (
<figureCitation box="[458,540,1906,1931]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1406,210,1768]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Kusala (Scodela) directa sp. nov. a. 2S abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. anal tube appendage and pygofer dorso-lateral inner ridge; d. subgenital plate, style and connective; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. style, dorsal view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, caudal view" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2608003/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[511,540,1907,1931]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="kg" metricValue="2.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="265" unit="g" value="2.0">2g</quantity>
</figureCitation>
) lamellate, manubrium very broad. Aedeagal shaft (
<figureCitation box="[1133,1242,1906,1931]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1406,210,1768]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 2. Kusala (Scodela) directa sp. nov. a. 2S abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. anal tube appendage and pygofer dorso-lateral inner ridge; d. subgenital plate, style and connective; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. style, dorsal view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, caudal view" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2608003/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="265">Figs 2h, i</figureCitation>
) relatively broad in lateral view, curved doro-cephalad, dorso-distal margin slightly expanded and serrated distally; dorsal apodeme large, Y-shaped in caudal view; preatrium short; gonopore on ventral margin.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
